Package: tidypq
Title: Tidyverse-Style Verbs for 'phyloseq' Objects
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Adrien", "Taudière", , "adrien.taudiere@zaclys.net", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1088-1182"))
Description: Tidyverse-style verbs for manipulating 'phyloseq'
    objects at four scales: samples, taxa, occurrences, and tree. Functions
    follow a consistent naming convention and support data masking for
    intuitive filtering, selection, and mutation operations. Designed for
    metabarcoding analyses, it integrates with 'MiscMetabar' and the
    'pqverse' ecosystem.
License: AGPL-3
